@startuml
title Stays4Pilgrims - Frontend and backend communication overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

component "Stays4Pilgrims Frontend" as FE
component "Stays4Pilgrims Backend" as BE

FE --> BE : Auth
FE --> BE : Accomodation browsing
FE --> BE : Comments
FE --> BE : Favorites / Suggestions
FE --> BE : Uploads
FE --> BE : Account updates
FE --> BE : Contact form
FE --> BE : Moderation actions

note bottom of FE
  Detailed flows:
  - communication-auth-flow.puml
  - communication-Accomodation-flow.puml
  - communication-suggestions-flow.puml
  - communication-media-moderation-flow.puml
  - communication-contact-flow.puml
end note

note bottom of BE
  Main API groups:
  /auth
  /accounts
  /Accomodations
  /comments
  /favorites
  /suggestions
  /upload
  /contact
end note

@enduml
